item.title: Reebok Floatathon
item.description: The marathon. How an average runner becomes more than average. I don’t really remember when I started caring about fitness but it was vaguely at the start of this year, I think. I have ( was would be more appropriate, perhaps :P) been over confident when it came to gaining weight. “Oh! I never really gain weight” was something common you would hear from me whilst gobbling calories consciously others might give a second thought to.
